name: Snaps EP
description:
the latest 4 tracks teaser EP is a juicy, exotic and tighten up garage-punk with tighten up melodies and the middle eastern twist

Recorded in July 2011 in Goldsteins Studios in Tel Aviv
Mixed by Nico & Konrad in Dresden, Germany
Mastered by Daniel Hajji Husayn in London, UK
out on Yakuzzi Tapes (Spastic Fantastic Records) from Germany on August 2011

high quility printed on a hard papers, baby blue cases with pink tapes + a MP3 download code !

Listen to the whole EP here - http://soundcloud.com/uzbeks/sets/uzbeks-snaps-e-p

name: Goggles & Flipflops LP
description:
2010's first debut LP from almighty Uzbeks
30 minutes of frisky catchy and tricky punk rock n roll

Recorded in Oz Studios in Tel Aviv, Israel in July 2010.
Mixed & Mastered by Robin Völkert in Münster, Germany.
Co-released by 6 record labels: Twintoe, Urban Decay, Dingelbarry, Partygarage, That Lux Good & Subwix on September 2010.

Pink OR Yellow 12" vinyl

Listen to the whole LP here  - http://soundcloud.com/twintoe/sets/uzbeks-goggles-flipflops/
